description: The legend of the Aokigahara forest (which lies just outside of Tokyo) says that those who have committed suicide in the massive wilderness are cursed to have their souls trapped within its very roots. Unfortunately for Alan, his girlfriend, Masami, committed her suicide there and she's now on a vengeful mission to ruin his life!
name: TPB

description: Envy's in big trouble on her latest gig, cataloguing evidence for a big case. Her kleptomania gets the best of her and she gets caught by Jimmy. But Jimmy's got troubles of his own and, after a struggle for control by his personalities, he forgets about Envy. But it's only a matter of time before he realizes that she's slipped away. Now Envy's trapped in the 31st Precinct, handcuffed, and alone. Although, like Jimmy, Envy is never alone. Can she and Sympathy find the keys before Jimmy finds them?
name: The Real Me Part 2

description: Hunter and Sons Funeral Home has been a family owned institution for three generations. For them a death in the family is more than the loss of a loved one, but the loss of an employee as well. Between planning their cousin's funeral and working six others, no one is left to collect new customers. Enter Envy Saint-Claire. While picking up dead bodies at such exotic locations as nursing homes, hospitals, and morgues; her curiosity gets the better of her and a trip into an empty coffin quickly turns desperate when she cannot open the lid from the inside. Now she's on her way to the crematorium, where her quick nap could turn into the big sleep.
name: A Dirt Nap

description: The curtain is raised on the biggest and best TRANSFORMERS game in history! See never-before-revealed art from the genre-smashing TRANSFORMERS: FALL OF CYBERTRON! Watch as OPTIMUS PRIME, GRIMLOCK, BUMBLEBEE, and SHOCKWAVE grow from conceptual sketches into finished, fully-realized characters; witness the development of CYBERTRON into the most detailed renderings of the planet that have ever existed; learn the behind-the-scenes secrets from the visionary artists at Activision and High Moon Studios! THE ART OF TRANSFORMERS: FALL OF CYBERTRON is a must-have for any fan of Transformers, gaming, or great art!
name: HC

volume.name: The Art of Transformers: Fall of Cybertron

description:
Alex Barnaby and Sam Hooker are back together and fighting crime the only way they know how -- by leaving a trail of chaos, panic, and disorder. Alex, an auto mechanic and spotter for racecar driver Sam Hooker, is drawn to trouble like a giant palmetto bug to a day-old taco. Unfortunately, she's also drawn to Hooker in the same fashion. There's no steering clear of trouble or Hooker when friends Rosa and Felicia call for help. A man has gone missing, and in order to find him Barnaby and Hooker will have to go deep into the underbelly of Miami and southern Florida, surviving Petro Voodoo, explosions, gift-wrapped body parts, a deadly swamp chase, and Hooker's mom.

Make sure to check out our Troublemaker video interview with Janet & Alex Evanovich!

Troublemaker is a #1 New York Times best-selling hardcover graphic novel!

Janet Evanovich, author of Finger Lickin' Fifteen, continues her New York Times best-selling Barnaby series with her very first graphic novel!

Written by Janet and Alex Evanovich, and illustrated by Jolle Jones (Dr. Horrible)!

Janet Evanovich has been a #1 New York Times bestseller fourteen times, and her novels have sold over 90 million copies.

The first graphic novel from author Janet Evanovich!
name: Book One
